Hi,
=20
I've been using Radiance on and off for about 7 years on a variety of
platforms.  I am getting going again after a bit of a hiatus and was
interested in what machines are currently thought of as providing the
fastest rendering times.  I have Radiance running on OSX and Linux
boxes, but they are older G3 and Xeon 500 cpus.  Anyone have any
thoughts? =20
=20
Thanks,
=20
Robert Westling


